{"id":"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA","title":"NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA","contents":"<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA\", \"name\": \"NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/schema.ts#L47-L48\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"no_errors_schema\">NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#no_errors_schema\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label const\">const</label>\n  </header>\n  \n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"bz44go68qv2r2ihtwrg7r83l3\">定義一個架構，該架構允許任何元素上的任何屬性。</p>\n\n    <p><a href=\"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#description\">檢視更多...</a></p>\n  </section>\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n  const <a href=\"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA\" class=\"code-anchor\">NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA</a>: <a href=\"api/core/SchemaMetadata\" class=\"code-anchor\">SchemaMetadata</a>;\n  </code-example>\n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7kppd6n5h382idiy593b71sdl\">此模式允許你忽略與範本中任何未知元素或屬性相關的錯誤。通常不鼓勵使用此模式，因為它會阻止有用的驗證，並且可能會在你的範本中隱藏真正的錯誤。考慮改用\n<code><a href=\"api/core/CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA\" class=\"code-anchor\">CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA</a></code>。</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/NgModule\n - api/core/SchemaMetadata\n - guide/testing-components-scenarios\n - guide/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/CUSTOM_ELEMENTS_SCHEMA\n - api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#description\n - api/core/NO_ERRORS_SCHEMA#no_errors_schema\n - api/core/SchemaMetadata\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/tree/17.3.0-next.1/packages/core/src/metadata/schema.ts#L47-L48\n-->"}